name: Under-one-minute-Tale
description:
Undertale resumed in a one minute game. Made for the  Micro Fangame Jam.

Game made withAdam Ledoux app Bitsy.

Audio added with Mark Wonnacott app.

Undertale is a game by Toby Fox, song is Snowdin Town theme from Undertale OST by Toby Fox. Cursed it with Reasynth on Reaper.
